longBusinessSummary: Qian Hu Corporation Limited, together with its subsidiaries, provides ornamental fish services primarily in Singapore, other Asian countries, Europe, and internationally. It operates through Fish, Accessories, and Plastics segments. The company engages in the total ornamental fish process, which includes import, export, breeding, quarantine, conditioning, farming, wholesale, and distribution activities offering various species and varieties of ornamental fish/ seafood directly to 80 countries and cities, as well as distributes to domestic retailers and exporters. It also manufactures and distributes aquarium and pet accessories under the company's proprietary brands and for 10 major manufacturers and principals to local retailers and wholesalers. In addition, the company operates chain store concept under the Qian Hu -- The Pet Family brand. Further, it is involved in the manufacture and distribution of plastic bags for the ornamental fish, food, electronics, and healthcare industries; and distribution of artificial intelligence powered aquaculture solutions. The company was founded in 1988 and is based in Singapore.
